name: Box Brown

deck: Griffin is a Boston, MA based illustrator. Besides the comics Baby and Healed he is best known for his male pinup and character crossover prints. He can be found attending many comic conventions in the North East United States. His company name is Shaded Areas Illustration with the motto "You think it. I'll ink it."
